org.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM roles WHERE roles.id IN (SELECT roles.id FROM users LEFT OUTER JOIN members ON users.id = members.user_id AND members.project_id IS NULL LEFT OUTER JOIN member_roles ON members.id = member_roles.member_id LEFT OUTER JOIN roles ON roles.id = member_roles.role_id WHERE users.id = 112) LIMIT 1
